---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<ContentSection title="Train Chatbots In-House" id="intro">
  <Icon slot="eyebrow" name="logomark" class="size-32" />
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    Chat.dev is a low-code platform for building
    <span class="text-primary">smart</span> chatbots with
    <span class="text-primary">state-of-the-art</span>
    foundational <span class="text-primary">AI models</span>.
  </Fragment>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-3">
    <a
      href="https://docs.astro.build/"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon name="mdi:document" class="size-8" />
      <span>Read the docs</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://chat.dev"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon name="mdi:tune" class="size-8" />
      <span>Start fine-tuning</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://hqmelywdmux.typeform.com/to/Igbg4n9V"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon name="mdi:contact" class="size-8" />
      <span>Contact Sales</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</ContentSection>
